{"type": "article", "id": 30542, "title": "办公室花盆系统", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-03T23:04:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160803214237kaIhqzWfr3epC4B2.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>来自杭州的 Siyu Lou 和何鑫发现比起和同事面对面聊天，人们更喜欢用手机在虚拟世界进行对话。为此他们共同设计了一款名为<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/27906329/LUEJIA-Flower-Pot\" rel=\"nofollow\">绿加</a>的办公室花盆系统，希望通过这种协作种植的方式创造话题，以此增进同事间的关系。这套系统包含四种不同的花盆和一个白色的展架，花盆内置了光敏以及土壤湿度探测器，它们会为不同植物的生长情况进行评估。当花盆电量较少、植物缺水或者阳光的时候，花盆底部的 LED 灯带就会点亮相应的颜色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803214301cXwe7upghJGsEiFm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608032143018MQp9AZobzdfHVY7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608032143017IRUpraBLwDmx9CJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803214302UA0zOqjFwo3HrTGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}